<br>
Luclin gave us SoFB, Mael of Electricity, and the Ancient Shock of the Sun.  Sounds like better nukes to me.  PoP is offering more, although it's kind of incremental rather than gamebreaking.<br>
<br>
Also, give me your definition of class balance for magicians.  In my eyes, it's using the balance of our abilities to noticeably impact solo, groups, and raids.  With Luclin we do all three rather well.  We certainly need a little tweaking and bug fixing, maybe some more damage in the form of pets, ds, and dd's.<br>
